## About the groupaccident service

### Start the local application 

1. Start a postgress-DB with gradle scripts -> createContainerPostgres (docker must be running)

2. Start the file service

3. Start this application: ```./gradlew bootRun -Dspring.profiles.active=dev```

4. Use Swagger-UI for testing the API without the client: [![Swagger-UI](http://localhost:8080/groupaccident/swagger-ui/index.html?url=/groupaccident/v3/api-docs&validatorUrl=&metric=alert_status)](http://localhost:8080/groupaccident/swagger-ui/index.html?url=/groupaccident/v3/api-docs&validatorUrl=)
